      "side": 1,
      "message": "i think there is a simpler way to do this, with less assumptions: try to unmarhsal json.RawMessage to TestFields and check its fields. On failure, treat it as a intermediate node.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 141,
        "startChar": 4,
