        "id": 1157909
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-08-13T06:26:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it\u0027s actually a valid assumption that only the leaves of the trie have \"actual\" and \"expected\".\n\nThough the function name hasRequiredFieldKeys is a little vague to me, how about something like isLeaf, isResultsForOneTest, isTestFieldsCompatible...",
      "parentUuid": "b4a88158_5fab1354",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 141,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 141,
        "endChar": 24
      },
      "revId": "20ddf50b6d3ca3513ddca781b3175df6261dedec",
